reviewText: it doesn't get any better than this

i like this series very much. The actors just seemed better than the ones today. Dont all older say that? Ha ha ha.
You like it or not.

Barney Miller seems as topical and hilarious today as it did when it first aired. The set is a good transfer to DVD, and the packaging is convenient and of nice quality. Seems like every time we run through this set we find new things to laugh at. It's eternal.
